OL,5,CHEN-ERGY POWER HITS EUROPE!    U   (%  
OL,6,                              WW       \
OL,7, A British firm which turnsCpoultry dung
OL,8,Cinto electricityGis expanding into     
OL,9, Italy in a #115 million development.   
OL,11, Family-runCFibrowattGis setting up     
OL,12, three power stations in Venice, Verona 
OL,13, and Cesena and 800 local farmers will  
OL,14, supply the manure for fuel.            
OL,16, The company's managing director,CRupert
OL,17,CFraserGtold Teletext: "This eco-       
OL,18, friendly project, piloted in the UK is 
OL,19, set to take Europe by storm!"          
