OL,5,CHEN-ERGY POWER HITS EUROPE!    U   (%  
OL,6,                              WW       \
OL,7, Fibrowatt runs two "hen-ergy plants" in
OL,8, the UK. The first plant at Eye in      
OL,9,CSuffolkGuses 130,000 tons of waste a   
OL,10, year from 12.5 million chickens and    
OL,11, produces enough power for 12,500 homes.
OL,13, "Our second plant inCGlanfordGproduces 
OL,14, electricity for 14,000 homes. A third  
OL,15, plant is being built inCNorfolk,"Gsays 
OL,16, spokesman Rupert Fraser.               
OL,18, "Our Norfolk plant should provide      
OL,19, enough electricity forC35,000 homes."  
