OL,7, The concept behind Fibrowatt has the   
OL,8, support of theCEuropean UnionGwhich    
OL,9, wants a fifth of electricity to be made
OL,10, from renewable sources by 2020.        
OL,12, "But there are many other benefits. For
OL,13, starters,CpollutionGfrom existing      
OL,14, disposal methods will be reduced," says
OL,15, spokesman Rupert Fraser.               
OL,17, "Until now dung has been kept in the   
OL,18, open whichCleached nitratesGand other  
OL,19, pollutants into the atmosphere."       
