OL,7, "Fibrowatt contributes to the reduction
OL,8, of theCgreenhouse effect,"Gspokesman   
OL,9, Rupert Fraser says.                    
OL,11, "By using renewable fuel the emission  
OL,12, of carbon dioxide and equivalent green-
OL,13, house gases isCtwo thirds lessGthan    
OL,14, that produced by coal-fired plants.    
OL,16, "In addition the ash produced by the   
OL,17, process is sold to farmers as an       
OL,18, environmentally friendly, nitrogen-free
OL,19,Cfertiliser,Grich in phosphate."        
