OL,7, The litter used by Fibrowatt comes from
OL,8,Cbroiler poultry farmsGwhere the birds  
OL,9, live in large, open-plan houses on a   
OL,10, bed of deep litter.                    
OL,12, Spokesman Rupert Fraser says: "Material
OL,13, from battery farms is not suitable for 
OL,14, these plants so we're also promoting   
OL,15,Cbetter living conditionsGfor poultry.  
OL,17, "Reality isCrenewable energy works -   
OL,18, in fact one could argue it works better
OL,19, than conventional forms of fuel!"      
